# =========================
# Keep important source assets
# =========================

# Do not globally ignore:
# *.png
# *.jpg
# *.jpeg
# *.gif
# *.json
# *.csv
#
# Reason:
# - frontend/package.json and package-lock.json are required.
# - frontend/public or frontend/src/assets images may be required for UI.
# - Ignore generated image/data folders instead.